OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777745466
OL,3,CGrieving mother shares her story to
OL,4,Chighlight importance of vaccination
OL,6,FA Co Down mother whose son died from
OL,7,Fmeningitis is urging parents to make
OL,8,Fsure their children are vaccinated.
OL,10,FMaureen Ellson's son David died when
OL,11,Fhe was just a toddler- now she is
OL,12,Fspeaking out in the hope of raising
OL,13,Fawareness.
OL,15,FHer call comes as figures show just
OL,16,Fover 85% of two year olds are
OL,17,Fvaccinated, which is below the 95%
OL,18,Frate reccomended by the World Health
OL,19,FOrganisation (WHO).
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/5
