PN,44304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F443A1777745466
OL,3,CGrieving mother shares her story to
OL,4,Chighlight importance of vaccination
OL,6,FGeraldine Mallon, Immunisation
OL,7,FProjects Operations Manager, PHA,
OL,8,Fsaid: "You can get the vaccine for
OL,9,Fyour child at eight weeks, 12 weeks,
OL,10,Fand just after the first birthday. So
OL,11,Fjust to remember that you get your
OL,12,Fcall for your vaccine, go get your
OL,13,Fvaccine,"
OL,15,FMaureen is sharing David's story so no
OL,16,Fother family has to go through the
OL,17,Fsame heartbreak. Her message to
OL,18,Fparents is clear: get children
OL,19,Fvaccinated, because she believes her
OL,20,Fson would still be here if the vaccine
OL,21,Fhad been available
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/5
